#Summary: 
Citibike in New york is very popular amongst male subscribers. It is most frequently used during commute times on weekdays and used evenly throughout the day on weekdays. I would gather more data on female customers' preference in commute. I would gather more data on the customer base on weekend rides to see if the weekend customers are tourists. So that we can make bikesharing more approachable and attractive for female customers and also target tourists on weekends.
